    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;Saddle Up and Drive&quot; 是一款设定在1970年代的游戏，你扮演一位已经醉醺醺且负债累累的老车手的鲁莽侄子。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102690/extras/71d6b1b28240f3d2057a226836e1cb44.poster.avif?t=1770380550\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102690/extras/71d6b1b28240f3d2057a226836e1cb44.webm?t=1770380550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102690/extras/71d6b1b28240f3d2057a226836e1cb44.mp4?t=1770380550\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完整版游戏提供了大量任务、可购买的车辆以及各种附加地图。在演示版中，你只能使用一辆车，并在你叔叔农场不远处的唯一酿酒厂进行糖浆走私，参与白天和夜晚在繁忙道路上与县警的惊心动魄的追逐战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102690/extras/d2759d00abad7142059e56d8845c3daf.poster.avif?t=1770380550\" width=654 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102690/extras/d2759d00abad7142059e56d8845c3daf.webm?t=1770380550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102690/extras/d2759d00abad7142059e56d8845c3daf.mp4?t=1770380550\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索一个广阔的开放世界；在这款演示中，你可以访问整个中央地图，没有任何限制，还能发现许多有趣的隐藏细节！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102690/extras/d8f5f4a79892172c0c41395c34259b5d.poster.avif?t=1770380550\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102690/extras/d8f5f4a79892172c0c41395c34259b5d.webm?t=1770380550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >记住！这款游戏在使用手柄时效果最佳，但你仍然可以使用鼠标和键盘。Saddle Up and Drive 正在不断开发中，如果你想保持更新，请点击完整版游戏页面上的“关注”！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102690/extras/7de4fd6a3991802659b8863216a534b2.avif?t=1770380550\" width=598 height=598 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>注意！</strong> 本游戏仅能在 16:9 屏幕比例的显示器上正常运行，例如 Full HD、2K 和 4K。</p>",
